title: Stresemann new Chancellor
subtitle: Ebert appoints Gustav Stresemann of the DVP chnacellor.
view-if: cuno_slapped
max-visits: 1 
tags: event 
new-page: true 
on-arrival: chancellor = 'Stresemann'; chancellor_party = 'DVP'; in_weimar_coalition = 0; in_toleration = 0; in_grand_coalition = 1; foreign_minister = 'Stresemann'; foreign_minister_party = 'DVP'; interior_minister = 'Jarres'; interior_minister_party = 'DVP'; justice_minister = 'Heinze'; justice_minister_party = 'DVP'; labor_minister = 'Brauns'; labor_minister_party = 'Z'; reichswehr_minister = 'Geßler'; reichswehr_minister_party = 'DDP'; economic_minister = 'Raumer'; economic_minister_party = 'DVP'; finance_minister = 'Hermes'; finance_minister_party = 'Z'; agriculture_minister = 'Luther'; agriculture_minister_party = 'I'; transport_minister = 'Oeser'; transport_minister_party = 'DDP'; postal_minister = 'Höfle'; postal_minister_party = 'Z'; workers_kpd += 2
face-image: img/portraits/StresemannGustav.jpg 
  
= Stresemann to be Chancellor

The failure of Cuno has led Ebert to try out something new again.

- @join_stresemann: The SPD joins the Stresemann government.
- @tolerate_stress: The SPD tolerates Stresemann but won't participate.
- @braunermuell: The SPD will demand the chancellorship.
- @fuck_monarchism: Maybe the DNVP should have a try at ruining their electoral performance for once...
  
@join_stresemann
on-arrival: spd_in_government = 1; dvp_in_government = 1; z_in_government = 1; ddp_in_government = 1; in_grand_coalition = 1; leverage = spd_votes
choose-if: reformist_strength >= (left_strength) and early_dvp_cooperation >= 1 and dvp_relation >= 30

The SPD agress to join the Stresemann government.

- @selection_of_ministries_stresemann

@selection_of_ministries_stresemann
title: Select our ministries

We can choose a few ministries. Controlling a ministry allows us to directly effect policy in that area.

- @labor
- @interior_main
- @finance
- @economic
- @justice
- @foreign
- @agriculture
- @reichswehr
- @transport
- @done_stress
  
@labor
title: Labor Ministry
subtitle: Taking the Labor Ministry is expected of us.
unavailable-subtitle: We do not have enough leverage.
choose-if: leverage >= 5
view-if: labor_minister_party != "SPD"
on-arrival: leverage -= 5; labor_minister_party = "SPD"; labor_minister = "Wissell"
go-to: selection_of_ministries_stresemann

Rudolf Wissell of the <span style="color: #c00000;">**SPD**</span> has been appointed labor minister.

@interior_main
title: Interior Ministry
subtitle: Taking the Interior Ministry is expected of us. The Interior Ministry controls domestic security.
unavailable-subtitle: We do not have enough leverage.
choose-if: leverage >= 5
view-if: interior_minister_party != "SPD"

- @appoint_severing
- @appoint_sollmann
- @cancel_interior

@appoint_severing
title: Carl Severing
subtitle: (reformist).
