@tolerate_stress

@braunermuell
subtitle: We would surely be denied any ministries.
choose-if: z_relation >= 60 and dvp_relation >= 40
unavailable-subtitle: Our partners don't even consider this option.
on-arrival:{!
if (Q.prussia_leader !== "Braun") { 
Q.chancellor = 'Braun'; 
Q.chancellor_party = braun_in; 
} 
if (Q.prussia_leader == "Braun") { 
Q.chancellor = 'Müller'; 
Q.chancellor_party = muller_in; 
}
!}
spd_in_government = 1; z_relation -= 5; dvp_relation -= 5

The bourgeois parties agreed to let [+ chancellor +] ([+ chancellor_party +]) be chancellor.

@fuck_monarchism
choose-if: ddp_relation <= 50
on-arrival: dnvp_in_government; workers_dnvp -= 5; workers_nsdap += 6; workers_kpd += 4; unemployed_nsdap += 2; rural_nsdap += 5; new_middle_ddp -= 3 pro_republic -= 3; nationalism += 2; interior_minister = 'Schiele'; interior_minister_party = 'DNVP'; agriculture_minister = 'Schiele'; agriculture_minister_party = 'DNVP'

The DNVP just entered a national government...



